# drawGraphics()

## Features
- It creates the playing background for the game
- It creates the ball and players
- It sets the time limit

### Scenario: Create the window for the game

  Given: The interface is switch on
  
  When: The user gives the width and height
  
  Then: Create the walls for the game interface and also place the paddle at the center of the wall
  
### Scenario: Set the time

  Given: The game is working
  
  When: The interface shows the time select option and user selects one
  
  Then: Set that time as the end of the game
